            jobTitle="Software Engineer"
            imageUrl="public/assets/Screenshot 2024-03-02 at 15.25.03.png"
          />

          <FeedbackCard
            comment="Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Quia, tempora voluptates. Voluptatem deserunt consequatur minus, incidunt explicabo velit molestiae nam tenetur esse numquam delectus natus! Fugiat explicabo accusantium doloribus architecto."
